Package org.oddjob.scheduling

Different types of schedulers.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Keeper
    Provides a guard that allows only one winning Outcome but any number of loosing outcomes.
    LoosingOutcome
    An {link Outcome} for the looser.
    Outcome
    The Outcome of attempting to grab something from a Keeper.
    WinningOutcome
    An Outcome for the winner.
